values:
Apparently, had I of kept my application in the running, I would have gotten the job at Adams Farm.&nbsp; 
I'm glad at least that i'm marketable &amp; interviewed well.&nbsp; because I wasn't so convinced of it before.&nbsp; 
I'm quite sad I had to turn it down, but the pay cut just wasn't worth it.&nbsp; 

But I feel good.&nbsp; I have a plan.&nbsp; I have goals.&nbsp; I have things to look forward to.&nbsp;

i am the picture of normalcy these days.&nbsp; 

a house. a car. 2 dogs.&nbsp; great job. great boyfriend.&nbsp; hobbies.&nbsp; i'm happy &amp; well adjusted &amp; i'm settling down. 

&nbsp;it's freaky.&nbsp;
